 then I went to read it, the message was clear :hmmm:[/quote]\r\nYeah I got the same thing. The message itself was clear. The issue I had was, that I never noticed the red bar at the top of the page. I had started looking around, found Daves post in the thread telling me I had a warning and then I went to look for it. But prior to that I was oblivious to the warning.\r\n\r\nLike i said, it could be easily missed as I did miss it, knowing what Im looking for I now see them as I look for the red bar and Im expecting them as that was my purpose here to fuck around and get warned, but then I wasnt aware of its presence and didnt even notice it.\r\n\r\nSo thought I should mention that I missed it until directly told about it in a thread.\n\n[quote=mifune][img]http://i.imgbox.com/aduAOehf.png[/img]\r\n\r\n\r\nIs this what we are talking about?[/quote]\r\nYep.\r\n\r\nAnd despite how clear it appears, and how the fuck could I miss that, I did.',86439,'2012-07-16 18:08:52'),(44252,5714,84499,'2012-07-16 18:09:52','\r\nYou are talking about the bbcode assistant in the Post reply box right?\r\n\r\nisnt this exactly the way it works on emp.me currently?\r\n\r\nhow do you want it to behave? :hmmm:',NULL,NULL),(44253,5713,84499,'2012-07-16 18:11:30','\r\n\r\nhave you ever read your PM\'s on the current site? :lol:',NULL,NULL),(44254,5709,47234,'2012-07-16 18:20:36','I cant reproduce this bug either.  I get an initial browse page with links up t0 501-550 then next and last with last linking to page 601....\r\n\r\nFF 13.01 Kubuntu 11.10\n\nSame results in Chromium 18.0.1015.168 Build 134367',47234,'2012-07-16 18:22:40'),(44255,5713,86439,'2012-07-16 18:20:44','Ummm, maybe ...once.\r\n\r\n\r\nhangs head.\r\n\r\n\r\nNah seriously, Ive checked it plenty. On the main site, the heading \"messages\" always exists, so I became familiar with it immediately. I check my dl/ul as I sign in, so I always see the little 1 or 2 or whatever next to messages. Im specifically looking for it though. That red bar just didnt even register with me, and wasnt there when I first looked around (I think it wasnt anyway) so didnt know to look for it. I dont know why I missed it being that long and red, but I didnt see it.\r\n\r\nMaybe it should always be there, a shade of blue when nothing new, and red when its got new messages. Although, I think it takes up real estate and not being there (unless a message is there) might be more appealing to most.\r\n\r\nI see it now no problems, but Im expecting them so I look for it. But at the time I had never seen it before and didnt even notice it, so just mentioned that.',NULL,NULL),(44256,5670,86439,'2012-07-16 18:28:06','They say it makes you go blind.\r\n\r\nBut who takes that seriously?',NULL,NULL),(44257,5681,129045,'2012-07-16 18:29:46','Can\'t upload anything right now, but if you create a request that matches anything in this http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35141\r\n\r\nI\'ll use it to fill.\r\n\r\nAlso, since you\'re willing, I could do another test:\r\n\r\n- You create a random request\r\n- We vote some bounties\r\n- I\'ll fill it with a random torrent and claim the bounty (you\'ll receive a notification via PM) \r\n- Then I\'ll report it\r\n- The staff will unfill it and send me a notification (the bounty is taken away from me)\r\n\r\nWe then check if things went ok, you could test deleting and editing the request too, since users have no option to do that :hmmm:',129045,'2012-07-16 19:55:28'),(44258,5713,48010,'2012-07-16 18:36:14','I think this is solved :grin:',NULL,NULL),(44259,5709,129045,'2012-07-16 18:39:28','Is there a difference in browsing capabilities between users and Staff? :hmmm:',NULL,NULL),(44260,5670,47234,'2012-07-16 18:43:13','[quote=knickers]They say it makes you go blind.\r\n\r\nBut who takes that seriously?[/quote]\r\n\r\n :lmao: ',NULL,NULL),(44261,5714,48010,'2012-07-16 18:44:13','[quote=mifune]You are talking about the bbcode assistant in the Post reply box right?\n\nisnt this exactly the way it works on emp.me currently?\n\nhow do you want it to behave? :hmmm:[/quote]\n\nyes ok - I will just continue to add url tags by typing and not use the link in the editor - no problem  and forget this report ',48010,'2012-07-16 18:44:49'),(44262,5713,86439,'2012-07-16 18:52:35','Maybe it should flash... for the oldies.\n\nOr a hand could come out and slap me upside the head, \"oi, message\".',86439,'2012-07-16 18:53:57'),(44263,5715,48010,'2012-07-16 18:54:49','I have not had any !!\r\n\r\nwant to check the big red new meesage \r\n\r\nand also does my profile setting show saying \"Don\'t PM me for suport etc\" ?\r\n\r\nTIA Dave',NULL,NULL),(44264,5681,48010,'2012-07-16 19:02:28','was going to add a JA request \r\n\r\nshow stopper - I need to specify a particular category\r\n\r\nWTF ?\r\n\r\nadded to suugestions as well',NULL,NULL),(44265,5715,129045,'2012-07-16 19:02:33','Sent.\r\n\r\nYes, your profile shows that message.',NULL,NULL),(44266,5716,48010,'2012-07-16 19:04:14','Hmmm why ?\n\nIf I want to request why do I need to specify a category\n\nsee [url]http://empornium.mooo.com/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=2681[/url]',48010,'2012-07-16 19:04:31'),(44267,5715,84499,'2012-07-16 19:05:40','\r\npm sent.\r\n\r\n[img]http://i.imgbox.com/adyzxwel.png[/img]\r\n\r\nwhere it says \'mifune\' it will say \'Dave\' - [url=/user.php?id=48010]click on that and you go to your profile[/url]\r\n\r\n(yes, your profile is set from your profile at emp :wink:)\r\n',NULL,NULL),(44268,5715,48010,'2012-07-16 19:05:53','[quote=yamchan07bb]Sent.\r\n\r\nYes, your profile shows that message.[/quote]cool got the PM and thanks for confirming the profile thing',NULL,NULL),(44269,5709,48010,'2012-07-16 19:12:42','http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?page=601\r\n\r\nI see \r\n\r\n<< First < Prev | 29501-29550 | 29551-29600 | 29601-29650 | 29651-29700 | 29701-29750 | 29751-29800 | 29801-29850 | 29851-29900 | 29901-29950 | 29951-30000 | 30001-30035\r\n\r\nand links work\r\n\r\