ne I can\'t replicate, I had talked about a similar problem here http://empornium.mooo.com/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=2652\r\n\r\nBut after mifune corrected the Search boxes, the text didn\'t overlap anymore :hmmm:\r\n\r\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=C258_5009EF98][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/image-C258_5009EF98.jpg[/img][/url][/quote]\r\n\r\nyeh same thing happens in all my browsers.. starts overlapping at anything below [u]1140px[/u] window width. \r\n\r\n\r\ntop to bottom >> Chrome, Safari and Firefox. \r\n\r\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=3641_5009F383][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/thumb.php?id=3641_5009F383[/img][/url]\r\n\r\nim using a Macbook btw with default resolution of 1440x900.',NULL,NULL),(44536,5746,129045,'2012-07-21 02:37:06','Well, the culprit most likely is the text size. Toying around here with the CSS, I can trigger a similar situation :hmmm:',NULL,NULL),(44537,5746,84499,'2012-07-21 02:41:57','\r\nI am so tempted to just set the min page width to 1200 :lol:',NULL,NULL),(44538,5746,85111,'2012-07-21 03:13:48','[quote=mifune]I am so tempted to just set the min page width to 1200 :lol:[/quote]\r\n\r\nfunny you say that, i edited style.css and changed your header min width to 1150px and 1200px at that seemed to fix it. >>\r\n\r\n#header {\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    min-width:1150px; \r\n\r\netc etc\r\n\r\nhope that helps. lemme know if you tried to fix it n ill let uno if it worked on my end.',NULL,NULL),(44539,5746,129045,'2012-07-21 03:33:56','[quote=iamstoopid]funny you say that, i edited style.css and changed your header min width to 1150px and 1200px at that seemed to fix it. >>\r\n\r\n#header {\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    min-width:1150px; \r\n\r\netc etc\r\n\r\nhope that helps. lemme know if you tried to fix it n ill let uno if it worked on my end.[/quote]\r\n\r\nCan you try a lower font size?\r\n\r\nLook for [color=#330099]#menu[/color] and [color=#330099]#stats_block[/color], they govern the overlapping text at the top bar.\r\n\r\nThese are the safe values I tried, anything higher and it will overlap:\r\n\r\n[code]#menu {\r\nfont-size: 10.5pt;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#stats_block { \r\nfont-size: 8.5pt;\r\n}[/code]',129045,'2012-07-21 03:49:54'),(44540,5679,130545,'2012-07-21 04:18:26','gimme a crapload of stuff and ill use em',NULL,NULL),(44541,5746,85111,'2012-07-21 04:22:23','[quote=yamchan07bb][quote=iamstoopid]funny you say that, i edited style.css and changed your header min width to 1150px and 1200px at that seemed to fix it. >>\r\n\r\n#header {\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    min-width:1150px; \r\n\r\netc etc\r\n\r\nhope that helps. lemme know if you tried to fix it n ill let uno if it worked on my end.[/quote]\r\n\r\nCan you try a lower font size?\r\n\r\nLook for [color=#330099]#menu[/color] and [color=#330099]#stats_block[/color], they govern the overlapping text at the top bar.\r\n\r\nThese are the safe values I tried, anything higher and it will overlap:\r\n\r\n[code]#menu {\r\nfont-size: 10.5pt;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#stats_block { \r\nfont-size: 8.5pt;\r\n}[/code][/quote]\r\n\r\nyeh still overlaps, it fits when i change the stats_block font down to 7.5pt/0.6em it fits but not 8.5pt. Here\'s some screens. Also changing minimum width like i said before stops the overlapping and keeps the font large. \r\n\r\nThese are all valid fixes, font fix looks best to me but I\'m not sure how it\'ll effect other users aka windows users. \r\n\r\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=2BF9_500A10DE][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/thumb.php?id=2BF9_500A10DE[/img][/url]\r\n\r\n\r\nAlso i got a small bug on search box where magazine and masturbation appears underneath the tick box.\r\n\r\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=2D4B_500A11E9][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/thumb.php?id=2D4B_500A11E9[/img][/url]\r\n\r\nnot sure to post a new thread or just keep posting in this thread as most of the bugs im finding are alignment/overlapping things.\r\n',NULL,NULL),(44544,5748,130545,'2012-07-21 04:38:49','On the bonus shop, when I buy things, I think it would be nice to give me a confirmation that something went through whether through just a text box saying \"bla bla successful\" or a PM even.',NULL,NULL),(44545,5749,130545,'2012-07-21 04:42:29','http://empornium.mooo.com/collages.php?id=4\r\n\r\nWhen you create a collage, one of the options is a pornstar.\r\n\r\nI created one but there is no picture option available O_o\r\n\r\nit would be nice to be able to match the face with the name',NULL,NULL),(44547,5749,84499,'2012-07-21 04:49:55','\r\n\r\nYou can add a picture in the description area using bbcode.\r\n\r\nThe Cover Art area is for cover art of the torrents you collate in your collage.',NULL,NULL),(44548,5746,129045,'2012-07-21 05:00:13','Oh well, just troubleshooting :)\r\n\r\nAbout the labels appearing below the checkboxes, better start a new thread. I\'m using Win7 here, tried Opera, Firefox , Chrome and IE, I can\'t replicate that, even at minimum width :hmmm:\r\n\r\nTomorrow I will try looking into it on Ubuntu, to see if it beaves the same.\r\n\r\nEDIT: Yeah, no dice, Ubuntu also displays things ok.',129045,'2012-07-21 17:18:22'),(44549,5748,129045,'2012-07-21 05:15:06','Read here: http://empornium.mooo.com/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=2682\r\n\r\nTo check all the transactions you did, you can go to your profile and look at \"Bonus Credits\", then click on \"Show log\". It\'ll list everything you bought or received as gift from the Bonus shop.',NULL,NULL),(44551,5750,1507,'2012-07-21 08:17:48','[quote]Bonus Shop - You recieved a gift of -gb[/quote]\r\n\r\n\r\n[b]I got this from the system, and noticed that \"received\" is misspelled....\r\n\r\nusb[/b]\r\n\r\n:usb:',NULL,NULL),(44554,5753,85111,'2012-07-21 10:29:16','Doesn\'t matter what width the window is.. Magazines and Masturbation labels appears underneath the checkbox. Looks like a column width issue.\n\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=2D4B_500A11E9][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/thumb.php?id=2D4B_500A11E9[/img][/url]\n\nIts the same in Chrome, Safari and Firefox browsers.',85111,'2012-07-21 10:31:32'),(44556,5754,79930,'2012-07-21 10:32:05','Regarding the paranoia lvl, I have to ask if a user can hide it\'s uploaded torrents? For me it\'s kind of important to see uploads from specific users. I think it should be viewable by default and impossible to hide.\n\nps: someone can check if he can see what torrents i have upped, thx.',79930,'2012-07-21 10:33:40'),(44557,5754,47234,'2012-07-21 10:39:12','I can see what you uploaded but it might be a Mod Perv thing i dont know',NULL,NULL),(44558,5753,47234,'2012-07-21 10:41:04','Im seeing the same thing ',NULL,NULL),(44559,5667,48010,'2012-07-21 10:43:43','looking on emp.me forums this seems to be done already ? i will test later',NULL,NULL),(44560,5679,48010,'2012-07-21 10:48:39','[quote=inhalex]gimme a crapload of stuff and ill use em[/quote]\r\nyou just got a shitload of credits - you have 10 slots already so I didn\'t change that',NULL,NULL),(44561,5732,48010,'2012-07-21 10:54:15','[quote=knickers]Yeah, Im just picking on yas.[/quote]\r\n\r\nyou want your warning extended ?\r\n\r\nseriously it does help\r\n\r\nalso on emp.me it seems the irc has moved - will check later but hopefully it\'s better too',NULL,NULL),(44563,5755,47234,'2012-07-21 11:07:04','Have a look through and have a look through the tutorials forum too.  Tell em what you think needs fixing, changing or adding to Help and Rules links.\r\n\r\nThis goes for everyone :)',NULL,NULL),(44566,5754,79930,'2012-07-21 11:41:03','so any regular user... pls answer!',NULL,NULL),(44567,5744,103720,'2012-07-21 11:42:53','[quote=mifune]\n\nSay hi and ask any questions you have here.\n\nI can answer the first one... \n\nQ: what do FLS do?\nA: we dont know yet.\n\n\n:lol:[/quote]\n\nWell, this kinda sums up the whole thing doesn\'t it? :laugh:\nFrom my private tracker experience so far, \nFirst Line Support is volunteering to answer PM\'s about stuff, to ease the staff\'s load of work.\nFrom software stuff and coding, to simpler stuff like ripping, uploading, where to find covers etc. And other stuff, that people don\'t want to post in the forums, but isn\'t that important to bother a staff member.\n\nAs for access to staff messages and resolving reports, I don\'t know. I have a feeling these would be better off handled by actual staff members. \n\nSome suggestions/observations:\nThis is the FLS section of IPT\'s staff page:\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=8769_500A75CC][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/thumb.php?id=8769_500A75CC[/img][/url]\nPussytorrents, on the other hand, lists only names and the \"PM\" button.\nThere\'s a lot of text in IPT\'s section, but that\'s because of IPT being a general tracker, that offers help with OS and other stuff.\nSince Emp is xxx-only, only tracker/torrent related stuff could be listed. maybe there\'s no need to mention what every FLS member is familiar with (like in Pussytorrents\' FLS section), because xxx-only trackers don\'t have that many issues, as opposed to general trackers, but then again, I personally don\'t know much about connectability issues. \nSo, maybe the FLS people could make a post with a list of stuff they know their way around?\nOr a staff member can make a list of things, and FLS members say what they can answer questions for?\n\nAlso, note a foreign language FLS members speak, so people can address someone in their native tongue.\nAnd maybe a green/red thingy that shows if someone is online/offline?',103720,'2012-07-21 12:35:26'),(44569,5755,86439,'2012-07-21 11:49:40','[b]Ratio Rules[/b]\r\n\r\nLeech warning period is now 2 weeks, not 3 as on old site?\r\n\r\n\'If your upload/download ratio goes below your required ratio, your account will be given a two week period to fix it before you lose your ability to download.\'\r\n\r\nThe reference to two weeks appears twice, so I assume its an intentional change, but thought Id make sure.\r\n\r\n\r\n[b]Ratio Rules[/b]\r\n\r\nAnd this line has a break (between the words re-gain and your) (FF v14), where it would look neater if it just flowed as one line\r\n\r\n\'You will re-gain\r\nyour downloading privileges once your ratio is above that required ratio. \'\r\n\r\n[b]\r\nRatio Rules[/b]\r\nAs a suggestion, the method of calculating RR is somewhat complicated. From what i can tell, two people with the same number of DL\'ed torrents (snatches), but different number of torrents still seeding, will have slightly different RR. It might help if as an example, such a position was used to highlight how that continued seeding effects them.\r\n\r\nie: 2 people with 50 gig down, and 60 snatches. One with 20 still seeding, one with 48 still seeding. It might help to make how that works more tangible to the mathematically challenged.\r\n\r\n\r\n[b]Requests Rules[/b]\r\n\r\n2nd line, URL is borked, it remains text, not a hotlink\r\nDo Not request [url=/articles.php?topic=forbidden content]Forbidden Content[/url]! It will just get you a warning or your account will be disabled in extreme cases.',NULL,NULL),(44570,5754,47234,'2012-07-21 11:50:16','Moved to request tests so people are more likely to stumble upon it :)',NULL,NULL),(44571,5755,47234,'2012-07-21 11:53:44','[quote=knickers][b]Ratio Rules[/b]\n\nLeech warning period is now 2 weeks, not 3 as on old site?\n\n\'If your upload/download ratio goes below your required ratio, your account will be given a two week period to fix it before you lose your ability to download.\'\n\nThe reference to two weeks appears twice, so I assume its an intentional change, but thought Id make sure.[/quote]\n\n:dunno:\n\n[quote][b]Ratio Rules[/b]\n\nAnd this line has a break (between the words re-gain and your) (FF v14), where it would look neater if it just flowed as one line\n\n\'You will re-gain\nyour downloading privileges once your ratio is above that required ratio. \'[/quote]\n\nI will fix that now :) [color=blue] Fixed[/color]\n\n[quote][b]Ratio Rules[/b]\nAs a suggestion, the method of calculating RR is somewhat complicated. From what i can tell, two people with the same number of DL\'ed torrents (snatches), but different number of torrents still seeding, will have slightly different RR. It might help if as an example, such a position was used to highlight how that continued seeding effects them.\n\nie: 2 people with 50 gig down, and 60 snatches. One with 20 still seeding, one with 48 still seeding. It might help to make how that works more tangible to the mathematically challenged.[/quote]\n\nIf i understood it properly myself i might change this but to be honest i dont :lol:\n\n\n[quote][b]Requests Rules[/b]\n\n2nd line, URL is borked, it remains text, not a hotlink\nDo Not request [url=/articles.php?topic=forbidden content]Forbidden Content[/url]! It will just get you a warning or your account will be disabled in extreme cases.[/quote]\n\nHopefully i can find where i stuffed that and fix it :) [color=blue] Fixed that was my bad i changed the url to the article a while back due to problems with the space.  Looks like i missed updating one link [/color]',47234,'2012-07-21 11:57:17'),(44572,5754,103720,'2012-07-21 11:59:26','I can see two torrents uploaded by you, I3af.\r\nIs that right?',NULL,NULL),(44573,5754,79930,'2012-07-21 12:01:06','[quote=eimaimpala]I can see two torrents uploaded by you, I3af.\r\nIs that right?[/quote]\r\nYep, that\'s right. So I hope it works like this, it\'s important. \r\nty!',NULL,NULL),(44574,5755,47234,'2012-07-21 12:03:02','I can see im going to create a lot of work for myself with this.  Keep em coming.  Especially interested what you think should be added to tutorials :)\r\n\r\nI have started at so many articles now i miss simple oopsies so fresh eyes help a lot.',NULL,NULL),(44575,5753,1243,'2012-07-21 12:03:25','Made the font smaller. Everything is on the same line as the checkbox now in chrome and firefox on linux.\r\n',NULL,NULL),(44577,5750,1243,'2012-07-21 12:15:22','Fixed.\r\n',NULL,NULL),(44578,5619,1243,'2012-07-21 12:20:33',' :confused: \r\n\r\nI\'ve never had a problem with my password and have looked at that code several times now. Still can not find anything wrong with it. Are you guys [b]sure[/b] that you are using the same password as on the main site? The only reason I ask is because this problem has me puzzled.',NULL,NULL),(44579,5619,47234,'2012-07-21 12:23:44','Yeah Lanz that bugs going to drive you and Mifune to distraction i think.  But so many reports where there is smoke there is fire...\r\n\r\nIs it something to do with special characters or Length or something?  Those are the only oddities i could think of that may mean some peoples work but not others....',NULL,NULL),(44580,5756,85111,'2012-07-21 12:48:05','Clownius suggested someone may be doing a logo for you guys already and not to insult whoever did your current one but thought I\'d give it a shot since im pretty bored atm... here\'s something I quickly did in 20min.. no biggy.\n\n[img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/image.php?id=7A38_500A874B[/img]\n',85111,'2012-07-21 12:49:12'),(44581,5755,86439,'2012-07-21 12:58:18','[b]Upload[/b]\nMissing space after torrent!!.\n\nOrignal\nDescribe the torrent!!,simply posting a screen shot or a pic is not enough!\n\nCorrected\nDescribe the torrent!!, simply posting a screen shot or a pic is not enough!\n\n\n[b]Upload[/b]\nCan the list of approved image hosts be made hotlinks?\n\n\n[b]Upload[/b]\nPedantic, maybe.\n\nOriginal\n\"Always check that your image host is not on the banned list!\"\n\n\"Do not use them here at EMPornium or your torrent will be deleted and you will receive a warning.\"\n\nCorrected\n\"Always check that your image host is not on the banned list! \n\n\"Do not use banned hosts here at EMPornium or your torrent will be deleted and you will receive a warning.\"\n\nOr as one line, but I assume the double line use here is a back up for people who miss the first. \"Do not\", stands out.\n\n\n[b]Upload[/b]\nMissing space between -ALL\n\nOriginal\nDO NOT try to \"slip one by\" -ALL Torrents are checked on a daily basis!!\n\nCorrected\nDO NOT try to \"slip one by\" - ALL Torrents are checked on a daily basis!!\n\n\n[b]Upload, Dupes[/b]\nMaybe make Requests/Reseed a hotlink?\n\nAn upload is considered a dupe if a file of the same size and format has already been posted either as a single file upload or as part of a larger torrent. If the original torrent is no longer active please create a reseed request using the \"[b]Request / Reseed[/b]\" forums, if a reseed request hasn\'t been filled within 2 weeks you are allowed to repost the content.\n\n\n[b]Upload, Dupes[/b]\nFrom this point in the Upload Rules page, the topics being explained are not re: Dupes, but appear under that heading\nAnd theres a missing space between \'seeded, and at\' (2nd line)\n\nOriginal\n- Make sure your torrents are well-seeded,at least 3-4 other seeders before you stop.\n\ncorrected\n- Make sure your torrents are well-seeded, at least 3-4 other seeders before you stop.\n\n\n\n[b]Upload[/b]\nSyntax\n\nOriginal\nSince very few peers will want to download the same vid in multiple resolution these kind of torrents suffer from a unnecessary short lifespan.\n\nCorrected\nSince very few peers will want to download the same vid in multiple resolutions these kinds of torrents suffer from an unnecessarily short lifespan.\n\nor\nSince very few peers will want to download the same vid in multiple resolutions, this kind of torrent suffers from an unnecessarily short lifespan.\n\nI prefer the last one.\n\n\n\nNext syntax\nMissing \'r\' from \'your\'\n\nOriginal\nPlease make sure you upload is NOT on the Forbidden Content List\n\ncorrected\nPlease make sure your upload is NOT on the Forbidden Content List\n\n\n[b]Upload[/b]\nagain, pedantic, two lines makes the rules seem more cumbersome.\n\noriginal\nIf you see any rule violations please use the \"Report\" function.\n\nLeaving a comment on the posted torrent isnt going to help staff deal with it. \n\nCorrected\nIf you see any rule violations please use the \"Report\" function. Leaving a comment on the posted torrent isnt going to help staff deal with it. \n\n\n\n[b]Uploads[/b]\n\nNot sure if relevant, but\n\nIf you dont know how to upload or make/upload and post screenshots then check the Tutorial Forum - HERE\n\nLink (\'HERE\') goes to a thread by Dave here on the test site, but the tute links in that thread go to Old Emp site.\n\nCorrection, re: syntax \nIf you dont know how to upload or make/upload screenshots then check the Tutorial Forum - HERE\n\npost and upload are the same in reference to screens so their inclusion created a difficult sentence to read.\n\n\n[b]Uploads[/b]\nMissing space after comma\n\nOriginal\nAlways check these rules before uploading,as they are subject to change.\n\nCorrected\nAlways check these rules before uploading, as they are subject to change.\n\n\n\n',86439,'2012-07-21 13:22:26'),(44582,5755,86439,'2012-07-21 13:22:40','[quote=Clownius]I can see im going to create a lot of work for myself with this.  Keep em coming.  Especially interested what you think should be added to tutorials :)\n\nI have started at so many articles now i miss simple oopsies so fresh eyes help a lot.[/quote]\nIll move to them next. Ill just finish up the rules stuff so I dont lose my place.\n\nAnd anyone else reading this, dont assume Ive got them all. Im betting I havent. And Clownius needs the work. :lol:\n\n\n\n[b]Tags[/b]\nYou reference Big.Boobs as official, but the list indicates Big.Tits is the official.\n\n\n\n[color=#0033FF]EDIT: DONE[/color]',86439,'2012-07-22 06:51:10'),(44583,5679,79646,'2012-07-21 13:29:37','If ya still wantin em tested I\'d be willin ta test either slots or creds.\n\nSoon as I can figure out which tracker announce thingy to use (I be running on fumes brainwise today.)\n\n[Edit] Figured it out very soon after I posted this. But Thanks for the OTHER method Lanz, that would indeed be easier. [/Edit]',79646,'2012-07-21 14:46:45'),(44584,5755,86439,'2012-07-21 13:47:03','[b]Downloading[/b]\n\nPlease check the ratio rules carefully and watch your current and next step of required ratio.\n\nMight read better as\nPlease check the ratio rules carefully and watch your current ratio, and always be mindful of what your next step of required ratio will be.\n\n\n[b]Downloading[/b]\nAlways check your stats BEFORE you download anything. If you have a low ratio, you could grab a Free Leech torrent (which is designated by a gold spinning coin), or you could try downloading something new. Always grabbing what you want might not be a good idea as it may already be over seeded. It\'s a good idea to try and build a good healthy ratio first before you attempt to download everything you may want right away.\n\n\nmight be good to add that seed/leech ratios are not always indicative of seed potential ...\n\nSomething like:\nBe aware, a trap many members fall into is assuming that low seed/high leech ratios on a given torrent always means they have potential to seed data. While this is a method of selecting torrents to help ratio, it may not always be the case. If a torrent has more than one file, and a member only downloads select parts of it, they will never be shown as a seeder, they will always show as a leecher. You will not seed any data to those individuals as they already have all they desired of that torrent. Please be mindful of that fact of bit torrent life.\n\n\nOr maybe they should be simply referenced, with a link to a tute on selecting torrents to boost ratio. Theres not a lot in the rules section there, so its not going to clutter it up.\n\nAnd I just noticed a link to Getting Out of Trouble.\n\n\n\n[color=#0033FF]EDIT: DONE[/color]',86439,'2012-07-22 06:51:36'),(44585,5679,1243,'2012-07-21 13:52:42','Since this tracker gives you the announce on the upload page with your passkey, you don\'t have to download the .torrent from the site if you have filled in everything correctly and set the private flag on the torrent. But if you go the old fashioned way of first uploading the torrent to the site and downloading that one (which is the easiest route to go), then you can add whatever crap you want in the announce field. The server will replace whatever is in there with the correct announce automatically while downloading.\r\n',NULL,NULL),(44586,5619,1243,'2012-07-21 13:57:22','Well I\'ve looked it over several times, obviously I\'m blind to the bug but I\'m gonna take another look and see what I can find.',NULL,NULL),(44587,5679,87267,'2012-07-21 14:03:10','Give me some credits plz, I want to check if there are loopholes to gain illegaly more credits. but I need to experiment with some points for that.\n\nmaybe with custom URL editing like\nhttp://empornium.mooo.com/bonus.php?result=Your%20Account%20has%20been%20blocked,%20please%20donate%20all%20your%20credits%20to%20PornJacker\n\nbut then after bonus.php someting is you add manually in the url /bonus.php&setUsername=PornJacker&value=buy&itemid=3 would that work? maybe someone who DOES know PHP can test this?\n\n',87267,'2012-07-21 14:09:30'),(44588,5694,87267,'2012-07-21 14:19:06','are the collages removed from the header? \nyesterday it was there now its gone.. http://empornium.mooo.com/collages.php\n[url=http://empornium.mooo.com/collages.php?id=1]\n[img]http://hostinga.imagecross.com/image-hosting-18/9965Untitled-1.jpg[/img][/url]',87267,'2012-07-21 14:19:59'),(44589,5756,87267,'2012-07-21 14:24:37','What is the required pix size for the header? Then I\'ll give it a shot as well.',NULL,NULL),(44590,5681,85111,'2012-07-21 15:00:39','this may be a stupid question but how do i add a request? theres no create new request button or anything like that on the request.php page. same on the collages.php as well.. ',85111,'2012-07-21 15:02:53'),(44591,5753,85111,'2012-07-21 15:15:41','[quote=Lanz]Made the font smaller. Everything is on the same line as the check