be the official tag?\n',86439,'2012-07-22 03:06:03'),(44667,5765,1635,'2012-07-22 03:19:47','Received seed request for Layered Nylons 2012 by PM...well, actually have 25 seeders right now in reality. lol  However, I did not have the option to respond.  When I hit quote options nothing happened and shows error at bottom of screen.\r\n\r\nOnly options I had were \"manage conversation\" and clicking on this option nothing happened either. Hope this helps. In conclusion, I didn\'t have an option to reply to sender.',1635,'2012-07-22 03:21:46'),(44668,5755,129045,'2012-07-22 03:23:31','I probably forgot to apply some of the changes knickers proposed, sorry! :tongue:\r\n\r\nhttp://empornium.mooo.com/articles.php?topic=upload\r\n\r\n[spoiler=Test:]\r\n[bg=white,left]\r\n[bg=95%]\r\n[color=#0261a3][size=5][font=Arial Black]UPLOADING RULES[/font][/size][/color]\r\n\r\n[bg=black,left]\r\n[size=3][b][color=#FF0000][align=center]Torrents in violation of these rules may be deleted without notice![/align][/color][/b][/size]\r\n[/bg]\r\n[bg=#FFEEEE][bg=95%]\r\n[*]Failure to follow these rules can result in a warning, having your uploading privileges revoked or having your account disabled.\r\n[*]If a staff member tells you to fix something on your upload, you should do so immediately or your torrent will be deleted.\r\n[/bg][/bg]\r\n[bg=#FFFFEE][bg=95%]\r\n[*]All new uploads must include a proper English description and at least one tag. Adding more tags will obviously help members find your torrent much easier thus possibly giving you more leechers.\r\n[*]Do not add tags that reflect what is not included, such as \"No.Anal\" if its the only tag you are adding. Tags and filters work on positive results. Search results will show you what is there, not what isn\'t.\r\n[*]All presentations must have pics/screen shots that describes the content. If you post a siterip/megapack you have to post screen shots of all videos OR post a good amount and include screens to all videos in a separate folder inside your torrent for [color=#FF0000]selective[/color] download!!\r\n[*]Describe the torrent!! Simply posting a screen shot or a pic is not enough! Any torrent with a presentation with less than 2 sentences risk deletion!!\r\n[/bg][/bg]\r\n\r\n[bg=#EEFFEE][bg=95%]\r\n[b][size=2]APPROVED IMAGE HOSTS[/size][/b]\r\n\r\nAll users must use an APPROVED image host!\r\n\r\n[b]The following image hosts have been approved:[/b]\r\n \r\n[color=#0000FF][b]xxx.freeimage.us\r\nstooorage.com\r\nimgbox.com\r\nhotchyx.com\r\ncdnpic.com\r\nimageshost.ru\r\nfreeporndumpster.com\r\nimgnook.com\r\nshotpix.com\r\nspanknet.info\r\niceimg.com\r\npikucha.ru\r\nimagecross.com[/b][/color]\r\n\r\n\r\n[b][size=2]Private IMAGE Hosts[/size][/b]\r\n\r\nbringthescreencaps.com.\r\nrjm.web44.net\r\npostxxximage.org\r\n\r\n\r\n[b][size=2]BANNED IMAGE HOSTS[/size][/b]\r\n\r\nAlways check that your image host is not on the banned list!\r\n\r\nDo not use them here at EMPornium or your torrent will be deleted and you will receive a warning.\r\n\r\n[b]The following image hosts are banned:[/b]\r\n[table=45%,nball,left]\r\n[tr]\r\n[td] \r\n[b]adf.ly[/b]\r\n[b]blackassfest.info[/b]\r\n[b]dumppix.com[/b]\r\n[b]easyxxxhost.org[/b]\r\n[b]fastpic.ru[/b]\r\n[b]funkyimg.com[/b]\r\n[b]imagebam.com[/b]\r\n[b]imageporter.com[/b]\r\n[b]imageshack.us[/b]\r\n[b]imagetwist.com[/b]\r\n[b]imgchili.com[/b]\r\n[b]imgur.com[/b]\r\n[b]photobucket.com[/b]\r\n[b]piclambo.net[/b]\r\n[b]pimpandhost.com[/b]\r\n[b]pixroute.com[/b]\r\n[b]postimage.org[/b]\r\n[b]tinypic.com[/b]\r\n[b]uploadhouse.com[/b]\r\n[b]vfl.ru[/b]\r\n[/td]\r\n[td]\r\n([color=#FF0000]whole lot of nastiness[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]popups[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]popup[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]displaying wrong pics for some users[/color])\r\n([color=#660099]images disappear after one week[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]rootkit[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]popups[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]ppc[/color]/[color=#FF0000]popups[/color])\r\n([color=#660099]doesn\'t allow pornographic content[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]ppc[/color]/[color=#FF0000]popups[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]ppc[/color]/[color=#FF0000]popups[/color])\r\n([color=#660099]don\'t allow hotlink from here[/color])\r\n([color=#660099]doesn\'t allow pornographic content[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]popups[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]popup[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]popups[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]popup[/color])\r\n([color=#660099]doesn\'t allow pornographic content[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]pop-unders[/color])\r\n([color=#FF0000]Malware[/color]/[color=#660099]doesn\'t allow adult content[/color])\r\n[/td]\r\n[/tr]\r\n[/table]\r\n[b]And all other pay-per-click and POPUP img hosts.[/b]\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you want to have a pic host approved post a link in [b][url=/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=749][u]this topic[/u][/b], and Staff will take a look at it! \r\n\r\nWe encourage members to use [b][url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/]http://xxx.freeimage.us/[/url][/b] as a host for screens and pics here.  \r\n\r\nDO NOT try to \"slip one by\" - ALL Torrents are checked on a daily basis!!\r\n[/bg]\r\n[/bg]\r\n\r\n[bg=#EEEEFF][bg=95%]\r\n[b][size=2]DUPES[/size][/b]\r\n\r\nAn upload is considered a dupe if a file of the same size and format has already been posted either as a single file upload or as part of a larger torrent. If the original torrent is no longer active please create a reseed request using the \"Request / Reseed\" forums, if a reseed request hasn\'t been filled within 2 weeks you are allowed to repost the content.\r\n\r\nPosting a megapack or site rip that includes content that has already been posted (for the sake of completeness) is allowed as long as it contains a proportional amount of new material as well. When in doubt you can always consult a staff member for a pre-emptive ruling using the Contact link.\r\n\r\n*Split-scenes of previously uploaded full movies are not considered dupes.\r\n\r\nAlways do a search to make sure that what you want to share isn\'t already posted here!\r\n\r\nDuped torrents will be deleted!\r\n\r\n[/bg][/bg]\r\n\r\n[bg=#FFFFEE][bg=95%]\r\n[*]Always add an anonymizer in front of direct links to porn sites!\r\n[table=80%,nball,left]\r\n[tr][td]Format:\r\n[code]http://anonym.to/http://[/code][color=#0055CC]your link here[/color]\r\n[/td]\r\n[td] Examples:\r\nhttp://anonym.to/http://bgafd.co.uk\r\nhttp://anonym.to/http://egafd.com\r\nhttp://anonym.to/http://iafd.com\r\nhttp://anonym.to/http://www.brazzers.com\r\nhttp://anonym.to/http://www.naughtyamerica.com\r\nhttp://anonym.to/http://www.pornpros.com\r\nhttp://anonym.to/http://www.rk.com\r\n[/td]\r\n[/tr]\r\n[/table]\r\n\r\n[*]Make sure your torrents are well-seeded,at least 3-4 other seeders before you stop.\r\n[*]Use the [url=http://empornium.mooo.com/sandbox.php][u]BBCode Sandbox[/u][/url] before uploading if you are unsure about how to use bbcodes. Basic bbcode tutorial can be found - [b][url=/articles.php?topic=bbcode][u]HERE[/u][/url][/b]\r\n[*]DO NOT add commentary to your uploads making veiled threats that you will not upload unless you get comments or something else you seek...  If you don\'t want to upload, then don\'t do so...  Making veiled threats only cause more problems than they are worth...  So don\'t do it...!!!!\r\n[*]Multiple resolution versions of a file are welcome at EMPornium but must be uploaded separately from now on. Since very few peers will want to download the same vid in multiple resolution these kind of torrents suffer from a unnecessary short lifespan. Furthermore no bonus credits are awarded to the users seeding just one version of the video(s) contained in such torrents. We know this creates some extra work for uploaders but after long consideration we have decided to do what we think is best for the tracker. We are sorry for any inconvenience this causes but honestly think this will be for the better.\r\n[*]Please make sure you upload is [b][color=red]NOT[/color][/b] on the [url=/articles.php?topic=forbiddencontent][u]Forbidden Content List[/u][/url]\r\n[*]If you see any rule violations please use the \"Report\" function. Leaving a comment on the posted torrent isnt going to help staff deal with it. \r\n[*]If you don\'t know how to upload or make/upload and post screenshots then check the Tutorial Forum - [b][url=/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=2414][u]HERE[/u][/url][/b]\r\n[*]A topic to check before uploading: [b][url=/articles.php?topic=presentation][u]***Beginners guide to presentations***[/u][/url][/b]\r\n[*]Always check these rules before uploading, as they are subject to change. It is your responsibility to keep updated about the rules![/td]\r\n[*]No rules lawyering! Any wannabe rule lawyers will be banned.\r\n[/bg][/bg]\r\n[/bg]\r\n[/bg]\r\n[/spoiler]',NULL,NULL),(44669,5679,88640,'2012-07-22 03:26:01','I would also like some credits to go crazy with.',NULL,NULL),(44670,5764,129045,'2012-07-22 03:31:40','Can you describe in words what is the problem? Because, seeing the images, I can\'t notice anything weird  :confused: ',NULL,NULL),(44671,5766,1635,'2012-07-22 03:33:17','The upload is seeding fine and no problems with redownloading for seeding.\r\n\r\nHere is link to Upload:  http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35162&torrentid=30049\r\n\r\nNone of the images I uploaded work.  All have red X\'s in place of images.\r\n\r\nWith the exception of images not showing up, everything else seems to be ok:)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL),(44672,5764,115474,'2012-07-22 03:44:32','[quote=yamchan07bb]Can you describe in words what is the problem? Because, seeing the images, I can\'t notice anything weird  :confused:[/quote]\r\nAh yes, notice the Size, Snatches, Seeders, and Leechers, column? It gets resized when expanding the View Peerlist link below the torrent name and then returns to size when collasped. Those two are the ones I have found so far so I am led to believe that there are others that do it too. It\'s nothing major but something I noti