,':hmmm:\r\n\r\nIt\'s not simply adding [color=#FF0000].jpg[/color], the article describes how to edit the URL to gain access to the image without having it served through PHP, in other words: [b]direct link[/b]\r\n\r\nFrom what I understand, the system will only accept direct links. What\'s the problem with that?\r\n\r\n[quote]Besides that won\'t nessesarily work with other image hosts.[/quote]\r\nWhat other hosts? If they supply a direct link to the file, it\'ll work just fine.',NULL,NULL),(44991,5793,76180,'2012-07-25 00:03:11','Dave, there\'s nothing mentioning the stats in the PM.  I read that thrice to be sure.\n\nAnyway, thanks.',76180,'2012-07-25 00:03:30'),(44992,5800,129045,'2012-07-25 00:05:03','Without having to give up all the other information, couldn\'t the Tag list get a Hide\\Show link like the Cover area?\r\n\r\nOne at the top and another at the bottom maybe, for convenience sake on really long lists :hmmm:',NULL,NULL),(44994,5635,76180,'2012-07-25 00:11:20','I don\'t care much about the prices at the moment...I\'m more interested in the lack of 24H leech.  I mean, jack up the prices if it helps balance things out, but I liked using that feature once in a while to clear my list of things to download.',NULL,NULL),(44997,5800,84499,'2012-07-25 00:34:47','\r\n[mcom]\r\n[b]thread moved to Suggestions[/b][/mcom]',NULL,NULL),(45003,5802,1243,'2012-07-25 06:10:17','TÍÌ¯Ì²Ì Ì¦Ì†Í®ÌŒÌ‘ÌŽÌŒÍ§Í§oÍ“Ì¥ÍÍ‡Ì»Í§ÌÍ›Í«ÍªÌÍ¡ Ì·Ì¡Í”ÌœÌ™Ì¬ÍÍ‘ÌƒÌ”Í«Í­Í iÍˆÌ®Ì–Ì–ÍŽÌ¹Ì—Í“ÌÌ•Í¢ÍnÍŽÍ“Ì¤Ì¬ÍšÌ®Ì¾Í®ÌŒÍ¨Ì„ÍŒÍvÌ›Í‘ÌˆÍ—ÌŽÌÌ‡Ì’Ò‰ÌµÍ“Í“oÌ¢Ì¹Ì¦Ì°Í‡Ì¥Í—Ì‰Í’ÌˆÌÌ‡Ì’Í¯ÍÌ‰Í¢kÌ´Ì¨ÌºÌ™Ì±ÍÌœÌœÌ Ì˜Ì”ÍÌ¿ÌeÌ¯Ì¦Í‚Ì¾Ì”ÌÌ ÌžÌÌ¼Í‰Ì¦Ì¯ÍˆÍŽÌ“ÌˆÌÌÍ¤Í¦ÌŒÌŽÍ˜ÍtÌÌ–ÌŸÌ”ÌƒÌŽÌ€ÌÌÌ€ÌšÍ hÍ“Ì¥Ì–Í—Ì‘ÌÌ’Ì‘ÍeÍ™Ì³Ì»Ì™ÌŸÍŽÌ¬Í¤Ì€ÌÍ¯Í¢Í¡ Ì³ÍŽÌ„ÌˆÌÌ•hÌ¸ÌœÌ¼Ì…Ì‚Ì‚ÌšÍ¢Í iÌ¸Í‡Í–Ì™ÌªÍ‰ÌºÍ¦Ì½ÍªÍÍ¯Í‹Ì’ÌŠÍœvÌ´Ì¨ÌžÍ”Ì–ÌªÌ±Í—ÌÌ’Ì‚Í¦Í†áº»Ì½Ì“Ì‹Ì…Í¯Í¨Ì…ÍÌºÍˆÌ¹Ì®ÌºÌ­Í…-Ì¨Ì¢Ì—Í¥ÌÍ…mÌ·ÌˆÌÍÒ‰Ì¹Ì˜Ì°ÍŽiÌ·Ì¸Í”Í”ÍˆÍ¨ÌÍ’ÌšnÌµÌžÌ¯Í›Ì†Í’Í£ÌšdÍÌ–Í£Ì‘Í¬Ì”ÍœÍ  Ì¶Ì›ÌºÌ¦Ì—Ì™ÌŠÌ¾ÍªÌ‡Í˜rÌ˜ÌªÌ¯Ì“Í®Ì”ÌÍ§Ì‘Í¡ÍžÍ 