ross as backwards. Its also possible they are like that on every website using them.\n\nSmart, or smug would be closed mouth\nSmartass would have the cheesy grin.\n\nAt least I would have thought so.',86439,'2012-07-26 21:10:08'),(45302,5818,84499,'2012-07-26 21:32:44','\r\noh :lol: okay sorry that was a little dry for me to get, but i like laconic humour!\r\n\r\n\r\ner yeah you are probably right about the warning...\r\n',NULL,NULL),(45303,5827,86439,'2012-07-26 21:37:16','[quote=mifune][quote=knickers]Lady Ginga torrent   http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35177\r\n\r\nVoted down lady.ginga (was 3) (now 2)\r\nVoted down dildo (was 8) (now 7)  then tried to vote it up, no change\r\nVoted up anal (was 8) (now 9)\r\nAdded porcupine (added at +3)\r\n\r\nJust noticed the green bar telling me my vote was counted or some such\r\nAdded ginger.megs (added at +3) green bar states \"your tag ginger.megs added\" or some such. It disappears after a few seconds, maybe 2 or so.\r\n\r\nAdded tag, mifune.spanked\r\n\r\nGot red error bar stating already voted on lady.ginga when I tried to up the vote on that tag. That red error bar appears to stay, not time out.[/quote]\r\n\r\n\r\nIf a message is displayed when you return to the page then the msg will dissappear after a couple of seconds.\r\nIf you vote on a tag the messagebar stays.. if it dissappears then it gets really annoying if you are voting on multiple tags with the page jumping up and down :hmmm:\r\nIs it too weird?[/quote]\r\nWell its all academic now as you appear to have changed it, and its good like it is IMO. The two bars (Red and Green) behaved differently. Each time I attempted something within the tag rules, it would give a green bar and that disappeared after a couple of seconds. It was only the red bar stayed until I refreshed the page, or left and came back etc.\r\n\r\nNow they both stay until refreshed or reopened.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHowever, I just upped that torrent I mentioned earlier [url=http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35202#]Gabby[/url] and one tag I included in the original upload \'dildo\' was at 8 (normal), I voted it \'+\', and its vote count is now 9. I shouldnt be able to add a vote to it should I? I already got 8 votes on it.\r\n\r\nI also voted \'-\' on Shemale, and it dropped one vote too. ',NULL,NULL),(45304,5841,171777,'2012-07-26 21:41:06','I tested if the friend system works (and it does) but then noticed that none of the friends from the old site have been transfered. I know I had some on the old website prior to the point from which the current DB was taken so something must have gone wrong with the transfer.',NULL,NULL),(45305,5744,171777,'2012-07-26 21:49:18','Well thank you for adding me to the FLS. As my first act of abuse I am going to see about that annoying staff message. Now who would have had the stupid idea to post a bogus staff message?  :ohmy: \n\n[quote=mifune]As of now FLS have staff permissions for the Articles section, Reports, and Torrents Reviews (marked for deletion), and also they can see User credits & the seed/leech list for pervs.[/quote]\n\nOk my tool menu is still empty apart from a non working sandbox link so something must have gone wrong. \n\nedit: Yes I logged out. I also cleared browser cache and tried it in IE just to be sure. Nothing worked. Still the same empty menu.',171777,'2012-07-26 22:15:28'),(45306,5834,37338,'2012-07-26 21:54:33','So is it fixed cause I\'m no longer getting the 500 error but instead I\'m getting this now\r\n\r\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=B938_5011A0A8][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/image.php?id=B938_5011A0A8&jpg[/img][/url]',NULL,NULL),(45307,5842,129045,'2012-07-26 22:05:18','Read this http://empornium.mooo.com/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=2818\r\n\r\nThe user could create a request full of hope to acquire whatever material he is after, so he throws a good bounty on it to raise interest, but the request may never take off (or it wouldn\'t take off anyway if the bounty wasn\'t \'high\' enough). [b]But the damage is done, since the Bounty affects his Ratio directly\\instantaneously after being set.[/b]\r\n\r\nIt\'s too risky, I know Requests are locked to [b]Good Perv[/b] and up with a good ratio, but take me for example: I fit on the requirements, but if I was to offer a good bounty, that would set me back quite a lot. (ignore my stats here)\r\n\r\nSo like we do now on EMP.me, users could take the Credit route or offer the minimum Upload credit (100Mb) and throw a reasonable amount of Credits to keep it interesting for other users. I guess that would give users and their Requests a better chance without having to rely too much on the community adding to the bounty (which also may or may not happen anyway).\r\n\r\nPlus, with the new Bonus System, Credits have more value now.\r\n\r\nUsers could end offering a reward themselves and send the credits directly to the user that filled the Request, but that could end causing some trouble, since it wouldn\'t be covered by the system (e.g. if the request was unfilled for whatever reason, the bounty would reset but the credits would be gone)\r\n\r\n[size=2]tl;dr\r\n\r\n[b]Credits as a possible reward\\bounty option for Requests?[/b]\r\n[/size]\r\n\r\n[size=5]Your thoughts?[/size]',NULL,NULL),(45308,5834,37338,'2012-07-26 22:07:50','I see the torrent has uploaded. \r\n\r\nYet there are 2 problems with my upload. \r\n\r\n1) I forgot to get the announcement and place it in the torrent I created. I can\'t go back and edit that. \r\n\r\n2) When placing the tags on the torrent it says that whatever catagory is going to be placed on it automatically. Well when I did a oral tag search it didn\'t show up. ????\r\n\r\nhere is the torrent: http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35203',NULL,NULL),(45309,5834,171777,'2012-07-26 22:12:37','[quote=Wallabe99]I see the torrent has uploaded. \r\n\r\nYet there are 2 problems with my upload. \r\n\r\n1) I forgot to get the announcement and place it in the torrent I created. I can\'t go back and edit that. \r\n\r\n2) When placing the tags on the torrent it says that whatever catagory is going to be placed on it automatically. Well when I did a oral tag search it didn\'t show up. ????\r\n\r\nhere is the torrent: http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35203[/quote]\r\nThe first point is not problem at all since the tracker automatically adds announcement URLS to the torrent so it should still work.\r\n\r\nthe second point in a different type of error as the on from this topic so you best report it seperately.',NULL,NULL),(45310,5834,129045,'2012-07-26 22:13:40','[quote=Wallabe99]I see the torrent has uploaded. \r\n\r\nYet there are 2 problems with my upload. \r\n\r\n1) I forgot to get the announcement and place it in the torrent I created. I can\'t go back and edit that. \r\n\r\n2) When placing the tags on the torrent it says that whatever catagory is going to be placed on it automatically. Well when I did a oral tag search it didn\'t show up. ????\r\n\r\nhere is the torrent: http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35203[/quote]\r\n\r\n1 - The system will strip the torrent file of whatever incorrect announce you used and add the correct one automatically.\r\n\r\n2 - No idea about this one :hmmm:\r\n\r\n[b]EDIT:[/b] Beaten.',129045,'2012-07-26 22:14:21'),(45311,5843,171777,'2012-07-26 22:26:10','When voting on a request with the basic vote button I get the following message (no matter how often I click):\n\"Your vote of 20.00 MB, adding a 18.00 MB bounty, has been added\" yet the number of votes only went up with 1 in total. Probably to avoid abuse but then it should say \"Users Voted\" or something like that. It might also be nice to add that even the 20MB for has the 10% tax in it (hence the 18MB added part)\n\nFor some reason clicking it more often also just builds a list at the top\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=93B0_5011A72D][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/thumb.php?id=93B0_5011A72D[/img][/url]\n\nDuring this click fest the contributors list didn\'t update untill the page itself was reloaded while at the same time the field for total bounty DID update.\n\nAs usual all tested in Google Chrome.',171777,'2012-07-26 22:26:38'),(45312,5842,171777,'2012-07-26 22:30:37','Technically speaking the website uses 2 types of currency. Upload and Credits. I don\'t see any reason why someone should not be allowed to use credits for this. Credits however are often for many even harder to gain then upload so most likely only the rich would use it. And those people often don\'t mind missing a few gigabyte of their upload.',NULL,NULL),(45313,5843,129045,'2012-07-26 22:40:31','Same behavior on IE, Firefox and Opera. Adding a custom bounty will also have the same behavior, it\'ll show the notification but there\'ll be no change on the current page, until next visit or page reload.',NULL,NULL),(45314,5844,37338,'2012-07-26 22:43:08','Problem: Gang Bang/Orgy, cartoons, XXX Games and so forth. \r\n\r\nDescription: When trying to select tags for torrent, the selection is limited or missing to what you can put in there. Yet the Category list is filled with the correct listing as when viewed from the Torrent web page. \r\n\r\nNo screenshots do to the drop down box window in uploading a torrent',NULL,NULL),(45315,5844,129045,'2012-07-26 22:51:58','I guess this isn\'t really a bug, not all tags got copied, see Lanz post here: http://empornium.mooo.com/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=2655&postid=23986#post23986',129045,'2012-07-26 22:52:30'),(45316,5844,37338,'2012-07-26 23:03:14','totally different. A threesome and a gang bang are different. Yet there is no listing for gang bang or an orgy.',NULL,NULL),(45317,5845,37338,'2012-07-26 23:08:56','Problem: Tags are not automatically being added from the category\r\n\r\nDescription:  When placing the tags on the torrent it says that whatever category it is that it\'s going to be placed on it automatically. Well when I did a oral tag search it didn\'t show up. ????\r\n\r\nI have place this torrent in the \"oral\" category. When you select \"oral\" from the menu at the top it will bring the torrent into the listing.\r\n\r\nWhen searching for it by tag \"oral\" it does not come up. \r\n',NULL,NULL),(45318,5841,37338,'2012-07-26 23:11:49','I was thinking that since my friend is not a tester he is not showing up on the server. Maybe when the site goes live they will show seeing that \"we are testing a new site and server\"',NULL,NULL),(45319,5845,1243,'2012-07-26 23:13:09','Hmm. I see the upload and it has the oral tag and I could find it with a search?',NULL,NULL),(45320,5844,1243,'2012-07-26 23:17:28','As yamchan pointed out, the list is not complete. We have not spent any time on what tags should or should not be in the official list yet.',NULL,NULL),(45321,5845,129045,'2012-07-26 23:19:52','He mean this one: http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35203\r\n\r\nIt\'s missing the category tag.',129045,'2012-07-26 23:20:54'),(45322,5841,1243,'2012-07-26 23:20:54','No, that\'s a miss in the database importer. I\'ll add it.',NULL,NULL),(45323,5844,84499,'2012-07-26 23:27:58','\r\n[quote=Wallabe99]Problem: Gang Bang/Orgy, cartoons, XXX Games and so forth. \r\n\r\nDescription: When trying to select tags for torrent, the selection is limited or missing to what you can put in there. Yet the Category list is filled with the correct listing as when viewed from the Torrent web page. \r\n\r\nNo screenshots do to the drop down box window in uploading a torrent[/quote]\r\n\r\nwhen you select the category it tells you what tag will be added, for gangbang /orgy it adds gangbang, unfortunately I broke the bit that actually adds the tag on upload a couple of days ago it seems... thanks for the catch :gjob: fixed now.\r\n\r\nThere is an option for every category in the list I am sure, there is no cartoons category... there are hentai and manga categories though so.. :dunno: ',NULL,NULL),(45324,5744,84499,'2012-07-2