ase now went fine, logged correctly and a clear notification appeared at the top bar.\r\n\r\n[b]EDIT:[/b] And not a single byte was added to my DL amount. :gjob:',129045,'2012-07-28 18:23:07'),(45411,5848,171777,'2012-07-28 17:12:16','[quote=mifune]sorry I should have been clearer... I just added that tag as per your suggestion ;)\r\n\r\nas to adding a button for it, could do, but its a long tagname - It should be documented in the bbcode guide but a button is probably not nessecary.[/quote]\r\n\r\nNah button might not be needed. Afterall it will not be the most used tag around but it has great potential in the tutorials for linux and such.',NULL,NULL),(45412,5853,171777,'2012-07-28 17:14:07','I usually add most of that info in the description (which also shows up when searching for something)... But to specifically tag it? ',NULL,NULL),(45413,5849,92881,'2012-07-28 17:40:22','I can`t download anything, have no problems downloading on the old site. I tested my connection and I am connectible. On the individual torrent in Utorrent, it says the tracker is working. I`ve tried about 4 or 5 torrents over the last week or so with no luck. I`ve had one torrent up for 44 minutes still not downloading. I noticed someone else on the introductory forum had the same problem. Any help would be appreciated. \r\nI do like the look and function of this new site, obviously except downloading!! ',NULL,NULL),(45414,5849,1243,'2012-07-28 17:43:38','[quote=dpg3]I can`t download anything, have no problems downloading on the old site. I tested my connection and I am connectible. On the individual torrent in Utorrent, it says the tracker is working. I`ve tried about 4 or 5 torrents over the last week or so with no luck. I`ve had one torrent up for 44 minutes still not downloading. I noticed someone else on the introductory forum had the same problem. Any help would be appreciated. \r\nI do like the look and function of this new site, obviously except downloading!![/quote]\r\n\r\nThis would have been better as a new bug topic, but we need more info. What torrents did you try and download and did any of them have a seeder?',NULL,NULL),(45415,5849,48010,'2012-07-28 18:01:09','[quote=mifune]\r\n1) bad tags. what do you expect to happen?\r\n\r\n2) I cannot reproduce this. What exactly did you click/page did you go to? What actions precisely need to be taken to reproduce it?[/quote]\r\n\r\n1) yes it\'s a test so ok\r\n\r\n2) this is weird - the \"Dave reported it\" is not now showing in the torrent - as far as i recall i just clicked on the torrent and it appeared \"i reported it\" so i took the screenshot. Not much help but\'s all i remember doing',NULL,NULL),(45416,5679,80238,'2012-07-28 18:10:39','[size=4]Shit. Oh hell, let\'s just do what we always do. Hijack some nuclear weapons and hold the world hostage. Yeah? Good! Gentlemen, it has come to my attention that a breakaway Russian Republic called Fapistan will be transferring a nuclear warhead to the United Nations in a few days. Here\'s the plan. We get the nuclear warhead and we hold the world ransom for... ONE MILLION EMPORNIUM CREDITS![/size]\r\n\r\n[size=4][b]Don\'t you think we should ask for *more* than a million Empornium Credits? A million Empornium Credits isn\'t exactly a lot of credits these days. Virtucon alone makes over 9 billion Empornium Credits a year![/b]\r\n[/size]\r\n[size=4]Really? That\'s a lot of Empornium Credits.\r\n[pause]\r\nOkay then, we hold the world ransom for...\r\nOne... Hundred... BILLION EMPORNIUM CREDITS![/size]  \r\n\r\n[size=4]I will settle for what ever scrapes you have and hopefully you at least got a chuckle from my post[/size]',NULL,NULL),(45417,5854,48010,'2012-07-28 18:12:25','[quote=Lanz]I gave everyone 10,000 slots and 5 million credits, that should take care of that! :laugh:[/quote]\r\n\r\nthat explains why everything changed - I was going to add a bug but fortunately I read the forums first :grin:',NULL,NULL),(45418,5854,67255,'2012-07-28 18:25:05','Everything seem fine now',NULL,NULL),(45419,5849,92881,'2012-07-28 18:34:46','[quote=Lanz][quote=dpg3]I can`t download anything, have no problems downloading on the old site. I tested my connection and I am connectible. On the individual torrent in Utorrent, it says the tracker is working. I`ve tried about 4 or 5 torrents over the last week or so with no luck. I`ve had one torrent up for 44 minutes still not downloading. I noticed someone else on the introductory forum had the same problem. Any help would be appreciated. \r\nI do like the look and function of this new site, obviously except downloading!![/quote]\r\n\r\nThis would have been better as a new bug topic, but we need more info. What torrents did you try and download and did any of them have a seeder?[/quote]\r\n\r\nBondage Wonderland(MKV) http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=34735\r\nLez.Gone.Wild http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=34188\r\nLesbian Spanking http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=16699\r\nBlack on Black Lesbian pack - 29 Complete DVD http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=31206\r\n\r\nThe first three didn`t have seeders and Black on Black Lesbian pack had one. Now I just noticed that Black on Black Lesbian pack did start downloading, I got some of it. So does that mean we can only download those torrents with seeders. I thought oringimally it didn`t matter, that they all looked like dead torrents. None of the other 3 have downloaded anything. There aren`t a lot of torrents with seeders.',NULL,NULL),(45420,5849,84499,'2012-07-28 18:39:53','[quote=Dave][quote=mifune]\r\n1) bad tags. what do you expect to happen?\r\n\r\n2) I cannot reproduce this. What exactly did you click/page did you go to? What actions precisely need to be taken to reproduce it?[/quote]\r\n\r\n1) yes it\'s a test so ok\r\n\r\n2) this is weird - the \"Dave reported it\" is not now showing in the torrent - as far as i recall i just clicked on the torrent and it appeared \"i reported it\" so i took the screenshot. Not much help but\'s all i remember doing[/quote]\r\n\r\n\r\nI still dont know what you expect to happen about those tags... there is no mechanism to stop users adding stupid stuff like \'and\' \'this\' - do you expect there to be? maybe there should be... but Im not sure what you are driving at?\r\n\r\nAs it is users can vote those tags down and they will be removed when there score is < 1. Or staff can delete them.',NULL,NULL),(45421,5849,1243,'2012-07-28 19:01:11','[quote=dpg3][quote=Lanz][quote=dpg3]I can`t download anything, have no problems downloading on the old site. I tested my connection and I am connectible. On the individual torrent in Utorrent, it says the tracker is working. I`ve tried about 4 or 5 torrents over the last week or so with no luck. I`ve had one torrent up for 44 minutes still not downloading. I noticed someone else on the introductory forum had the same problem. Any help would be appreciated. \r\nI do like the look and function of this new site, obviously except downloading!![/quote]\r\n\r\nThis would have been better as a new bug topic, but we need more info. What torrents did you try and download and did any of them have a seeder?[/quote]\r\n\r\nBondage Wonderland(MKV) http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=34735\r\nLez.Gone.Wild http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=34188\r\nLesbian Spanking http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=16699\r\nBlack on Black Lesbian pack - 29 Complete DVD http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=31206\r\n\r\nThe first three didn`t have seeders and Black on Black Lesbian pack had one. Now I just noticed that Black on Black Lesbian pack did start downloading, I got some of it. So does that mean we can only download those torrents with seeders. I thought oringimally it didn`t matter, that they all looked like dead torrents. None of the other 3 have downloaded anything. There aren`t a lot of torrents with seeders.[/quote]\r\n\r\nYeah it looks like only black on black has a seeder and yes, if the