35\r\nLez.Gone.Wild http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=34188\r\nLesbian Spanking http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=16699\r\nBlack on Black Lesbian pack - 29 Complete DVD http://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=31206\r\n\r\nThe first three didn`t have seeders and Black on Black Lesbian pack had one. Now I just noticed that Black on Black Lesbian pack did start downloading, I got some of it. So does that mean we can only download those torrents with seeders. I thought oringimally it didn`t matter, that they all looked like dead torrents. None of the other 3 have downloaded anything. There aren`t a lot of torrents with seeders.[/quote]\r\n\r\nYeah it looks like only black on black has a seeder and yes, if the torrent doesn\'t have a seeder or a leecher with a partial downloaded torrent you wont get anything from it. Most of the torrents on here is dead because only people that helps out testing the tracker can seed the torrents here.[/quote]\r\n\r\nI thought I was helping to test the tracker, I got an invite to do so.',NULL,NULL),(45425,5849,1243,'2012-07-28 19:41:03','[quote=dpg3]I thought I was helping to test the tracker, I got an invite to do so.[/quote]\r\n\r\nYes and we appreciate all the help we get, thanks. Sorry, I didn\'t express myself clearly. That was not a comment against you, just pointing out that most torrents here are dead because we only have a handful of people here that seed any torrents on the test tracker.',NULL,NULL),(45426,5849,92881,'2012-07-28 19:42:59','[quote=Lanz][quote=dpg3]I thought I was helping to test the tracker, I got an invite to do so.[/quote]\r\n\r\nYes and we appreciate all the help we get, thanks. Sorry, I didn\'t express myself clearly. That was not a comment against you, just pointing out that most torrents here are dead because we only have a handful of people here that seed any torrents on the test tracker.[/quote]\r\n\r\nOK sorry I really like the new site, just need a bit of patience I guess, lol!! \r\nThanks for your help I apprecite it!!!!',NULL,NULL),(45427,5858,1243,'2012-07-28 19:43:25','Strange, I downloaded that myself to test the personal freeleech code and had no problem downloading it like that.',NULL,NULL),(45428,5648,129045,'2012-07-28 19:59:55','Mifune, Lanz... any confirmation on this?\r\n\r\nTried to look for a large torrent upped recently, but apart from the one in the OP (still not set as FL) the other one http://empornium.mooo.com/log.php?search=Torrent+30060 got deleted during tests to delete dupes.\r\n\r\nWith the filter implemented http://empornium.mooo.com/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=2805 ,  only 3 torrents are popping up and I guess they were manually set as freeleech.\r\n\r\nIf it still needs some stress tests, I guess I can hijack some torrents from EMP.me... for testing purposes off course  :demon: \r\n\r\n[size=2][b][color=#FF0000]EDIT:[/color][/b] OK, tested. Working fine, both torrents got FL automatically[/size]\r\n\r\nhttp://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35207\r\nhttp://empornium.mooo.com/torrents.php?id=35208\r\n\r\nRegarding this http://empornium.mooo.com/forums.php?action=viewthread&threadid=2615 , is 50Gb still the norm? Or you guys going to lower it to 20Gb?',129045,'2012-07-28 20:32:25'),(45429,5815,1507,'2012-07-28 20:10:59',':thumbsup:\r\n\r\n[b]Thank you...  :smile1:\r\n\r\nusb[/b]\r\n\r\n:usb:',NULL,NULL),(45430,5858,48010,'2012-07-28 20:13:16','I can DL it too with no problem',48010,'2012-07-28 20:13:43'),(45431,5854,1507,'2012-07-28 20:15:47',':thumbsup:\r\n\r\n[b]Welcum back 24hr FL slot...  :thumbsup:\r\n\r\nNow if we can only get that 1 Week FL slot put into place....  :laugh:\r\n\r\nusb[/b]\r\n\r\n:usb:\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL),(45432,5679,1507,'2012-07-28 20:20:14','[quote=DrkNess]well then either you 2 managed to cancel each other out or there is a max of 5 million credits that people can have at any given time.[/quote]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n:hmmm:\r\n\r\n[b]No, as I\'ve just added 105 million more credits 