iews\n\nfuck the fucking motherfuckers',49532,'2012-08-01 00:25:09'),(45725,5896,84499,'2012-08-01 00:22:01','\r\n\r\nwhoops lol.\r\n\r\n\r\nokay i wont look again.',NULL,NULL),(45727,5896,49532,'2012-08-01 00:25:24','[quote=mifune]whoops lol.\r\n\r\n\r\nokay i wont look again.[/quote]\r\nyou can look now',NULL,NULL),(45729,5747,129045,'2012-08-01 00:36:11','How is this not a bug? :hmmm:\r\n\r\nUse [b]Advanced Search[/b], select all your favorite categories, set some keywords and tags to be excluded and use \"[b]Make default[/b]\". There, all torrents will always be filtered by your standards.\r\n\r\n[b]Now let\'s say you need to do a unrestrained search...[/b] are you going to unmark every single category manually? No, just hit \"Reset\" (it\'ll not override your \"Make Default\" settings, but it will clear everything so you can do a clean search.\r\n\r\nBur this doesn\'t work on [b]Basic Search[/b], after using \"[b]Make Default[/b]\", [b]Reset[/b] is useless (it\'ll only cause a page reload, without clearing anything, so if the user wanted to do a clean search he would have to ditch his custom settings by using \"[b]Clear Default[/b]\" or start unmarking everything manually).\r\n\r\n[quote]Working as designed.  Bug can be closed.  Thanks![/quote]\r\nmicrofine\'s problem isn\'t even related to this.',NULL,NULL),(45730,5727,85111,'2012-08-01 00:45:11','yeh its all about the porn.',NULL,NULL),(45731,5896,84499,'2012-08-01 01:00:58','[quote=apparition]8908980989080\r\n\r\nwhen I first posted I got 2 view\r\never time i viewd it it incremented the view counter.\r\n\r\n\r\nwhen i edited i got 2 views\r\n\r\nfuck the fucking motherfuckers[/quote]\r\n\r\nthere was a bug on thread creation, it added +1 twice, fixed now.',NULL,NULL),(45732,5775,85111,'2012-08-01 01:07:08','this is great news, i\'m looking forward to creating my own collages when the site goes live. whoever thought of it is a genius.',NULL,NULL),(45733,5706,94952,'2012-08-01 01:17:30','I like this feature, 