quote]\r\nok should be done - let\'s watch and see',NULL,NULL),(45826,5904,84499,'2012-08-02 22:55:30','\nthe timer is not reset - but if a torrent is waiting to be re-checked by staff (to accept or reject the fix) it will not be automatically deleted.',84499,'2012-08-02 22:56:06'),(45827,5902,86439,'2012-08-02 23:39:53','[size=10]POTATO!!!!!![/size]',NULL,NULL),(45828,5891,49532,'2012-08-03 00:26:08','[quote=usillyboy]:hmmm:\r\n\r\n[b]If you close the search center, you can hide the categories...  you\'ll hide everything else as well, but at least it will look clean...  :laugh:\r\n\r\nusb[/b]\r\n\r\n :giraffe:[/quote]\r\nIf you close the search center then that hides tags too.  And no fucking way would anyone want to hide tags :smartass:',NULL,NULL),(45829,5910,49532,'2012-08-03 01:16:01','This sugestion is part of a suggestion dan made in http://torrents.empornium.me/forums.php?action=viewtopic&topicid=1948 I think it belongs here: \n\n\n[quote]  \nOne thing that would make [community] tagging easier, would be the ability to add tag to multiple torrents, returned by the last search (mods should also have the ability to remove tags from multiple torrents, using the same method):\n\nAfter a search, the browe page, would have a tag field, similar to the upload and detail pages, each torrent in the list would have a checkbox next to it.\n\nAll the tags entered in the tag field would be added to all the torrents that were checked, exaxtly as if they were tagged individually on the details pages.\n\nFor example: someone could search for [b]pure18[/b]. Then they could add the tags: [b]pure18 realityking usa english teen [/b]to all of them in one action. Another could search for [b]\"Sensi Pearl\"[/b] and add the tags [b]sensi.pearl cassie.nelson tiny.tits petite brunette flexible brown.eyes[/b]\n\nA mod could search for [b]FTV[/b] and remove the tag [b]amateur[/b], or search for the user [b]ImaVandal[/b] and remove the tags [b]sucky.video this.is.shit more.boobs uploader.is.gay[/b]\n[/quote] \n\nThe current tag voting system should be enough to prevent widespread abuse of the add feature (the staff can decide what user ranks should have access to it), and the remove feature will make the job of moderating tags much easier on the staff, any time they get a report of a bad tag they can search where else it was used and remove them all at once. \n',49532,'2012-08-03 01:17:17'),(45830,5911,49532,'2012-08-03 01:36:01','add  :ridicule: to their profile for 24 hrs  :laugh: \r\n\r\n:smartass:',NULL,NULL),(45831,5912,37338,'2012-08-03 04:25:46','Problem: When selecting the doubleseed button unexpected error pops up\r\n\r\nWhat I did: I tired it on all torrents and they are all popping this message up.\r\n\r\n[url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=7ACA_501B36DB][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/image.php?id=7ACA_501B36DB&jpg[/img][/url]',NULL,NULL),(45832,5875,37338,'2012-08-03 04:27:24','2.2.1 seems to be working fine. Never had a problem out of the latest version, I mean ever and I download from other sites that work just fine. Anyway, Knickers what bit torrent client are you using?',NULL,NULL),(45833,5910,73066,'2012-08-03 05:00:18','I think this sounds like a great idea.\r\nAnd it got me thinking about another feature.\r\n\r\nIn short, a tag auto system. \r\nLets say a actor has 2 or 3 names, adding one of these will auto add the other names.\r\nAnd a database that keep records of the artist name, where users can add other known names. This could also be used to add other tags like teen, english, brunette, tattoos.\r\n\r\nThis system could also be used to get similar tags to be renamed. Like some users add double.penetration while other add dp, this system could change dp to double.penetration or double.penetration to dp. and all the tags would be in the same kind of system and also a lot easier for the users to find what they are looking for. It could be used to change misspelled names and other stuff also.\r\n\r\nAnd some longer toughs...\r\n\r\nSo it would work like this, borrowing the post example from apparition\r\nSomeone would add sensi.pearl and/or sensipearl, this would be a \"actor\" tag in the database, another \"actor\" tag in the same post would be cassie.nelson and cassienelson for example. These would have \"trigger\" tags that could be teen, brunette, petite, flexible, brown.eyes, and also adding the main tags cassie.nelson and sensi.pearl if one of them were missing.\r\n\r\nSo adding cassie.nelson would auto add sensi.pearl, petite, brunette, flexible, brown.eyes, teen.\r\nThis tagging system could also be parsed in the old databases, some users could add stuff and create new tag auto systems that would auto parse emp and add and change tags. This would ofc be a problem with actors that\'s been in the game for a long time, and some description tags would be strange.\r\n\r\nExampel rebecca.liniares after boobjob and before boobjob would require different tags. So this system has to be a little bit interesting to get it to work. (but as an old database programmer i just think its sound fun) you need to keep track of the tags changed and also be able to remove and change those tags. So the system could have some problems that needs tuning and some separate stuff that keeps track of tags changed, so it can change those tags back if they don\'t get votes in the voting system. (great explanation from me) But the system could with no problem add stuff that doesn\'t change like brunette, flexible, brown.eyed, latino, russian, english and so on. If the system keeps track of the changes it make it would also be easy to restore of someone does a mistake or something.\r\n\r\nSo the rebecca.liniares example after her boobjob, someone would go in to the database and remove small.tits from rebecca.liniares, the script would then parse and remove all small.tits added by the program regarding this actor, unless someone voted for the small tits or added them in any other way (or they got auto added regarding another girl in threesome scene with another actor with small tits, or in a collection or movie)\r\n\r\nI\'m not sure about all the stuff in this, but the actor name stuff could be useful and the renaming of similar tags would also help. But in a siterip there would be a lot of tags. I don\'t know if that\'s good or bad, most of them will be similar anyways.',NULL,NULL),(45834,5875,86439,'2012-08-03 05:52:39','uTorrent 2.2.1',NULL,NULL),(45835,5912,86439,'2012-08-03 06:02:54','Confirmed. I just tried it on two torrents, got the pop-up asking if I was sure i wanted to use the double seed slot, click yes, then a blank page. No error messages though.  (FF 14.0.1  Win XP Pro)\n\nI reopened the 1st torrent page, selected the normal download and a screen pops up asking how to handle it (as expected I havent set it as defaulted action yet), and uTorrent pops up.\n\nI did the same with the 2nd one that failed as DS, this time used FL, the same screen about being sure popped up, clicked yes, then the handler message popped up and uTorrent handled it as expected.\n\nOnly 1 slot was taken from my slots, so its not taking the DS slot, that would be the FL slot I assume.\n\n',86439,'2012-08-03 06:07:50'),(45836,5904,171777,'2012-08-03 06:42:26','I can\'t seem to find where an uploader will be able to read the messages replied in the staff PM... Do they too get a staff pm notification? From both inside the torrent (logs) and the normal PM\'s there is nothing of the entire conversation that I wrote in any of the 3 staff PM messages yesterday. Also it is kind of hard for me to test this more in depth since I can always see the staff pm box... could i have a second account for things like this?',NULL,NULL),(45837,5891,171777,'2012-08-03 07:07:24','[quote=apparition][quote=usillyboy]:hmmm:\r\n\r\n[b]If you close the search center, you can hide the categories...  you\'ll hide everything else as well, but at least it will look clean...  :laugh:\r\n\r\nusb[/b]\r\n\r\n :giraffe:[