nd works the same for everybody. If some people are geting it, and otheres aren\'t, thats not good.',NULL,NULL),(46015,5818,49532,'2012-08-04 19:57:23','[quote=GaryE]I can not think of a single reason for the tax . . . I mean if the taxes were all put into a pile that was then used for something like bailing out new members or contests or whatever I guess I could make an argument for keeping the tax but that is way more trouble than it is worth.[/quote] I agree',NULL,NULL),(46018,5706,51063,'2012-08-04 20:06:48','I hear you I am not pushing for it either.',NULL,NULL),(46019,5818,84499,'2012-08-04 20:07:37','[quote=GaryE]I can not think of a single reason for the tax . . . I mean if the taxes were all put into a pile that was then used for something like bailing out new members or contests or whatever I guess I could make an argument for keeping the tax but that is way more trouble than it is worth.[/quote]\r\n\r\n:lol:\r\n\r\nwell that would be better than usb paying for it all out of his own pocket... it must be costing him a fortune!\r\n\r\n[note: not actually true, all the staff chip in out of their own pockets...]',NULL,NULL),(46020,5919,1507,'2012-08-04 20:08:56','[quote=apparition][quote=usillyboy]:hmmm:\r\n\r\n[b]Yeah, I don\'t know when they disappeared either, but it makes everything look spiffy now...  a cleaner look I think...  :yes:\r\n\r\nusb[/b]\r\n\r\n:usb:[/quote]\r\n\r\nAs long as it\'s intentional, and works the same for everybody. If some people are geting it, and otheres aren\'t, thats not good.[/quote]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n:gjob:\r\n\r\n[b]Yeah, this is true....  :smile1:\r\n\r\nusb[/b]\r\n\r\n:usb:',NULL,NULL),(46021,5919,84499,'2012-08-04 20:11:28','\r\nsomeone suggested columnless lists for torrents and I liked the look of it. The empornium stylesheet got a little neglected during development so I gave it some attention last week.',NULL,NULL),(46022,5920,171777,'2012-08-04 20:13:33','Only tried to generalise the layout of the rules a bit so far