ick on it you will select it:\n\n[img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/image-1B32_5022C139.jpg[/img]\n\nOther than having a number of useful information, [color=#FF0000][b]and now [you] pay attention![/b][/color]\n\nIt is best to input commands in this window especially the ones involving your password. So if you mess up with a typo you can avoid that the whole channel sees your password.\n\nAlso some commands given in the channel show their result in the status window. So when you go WTF how come I do not see the result of my command, check the status window.',70679,'2012-09-10 19:44:28'),(46442,5958,84499,'2012-08-08 21:31:53','\r\n[quote=yamchan07bb] \r\nAlso, the user Comments history needs a page title too http://empornium.mooo.com/comments.php , as of now it simply says \"Empornium Test Tracker\"[/quote]\r\n\r\ndone.',NULL,NULL),(46443,5820,51063,'2012-08-08 22:04:22','Resolved in another thread',NULL,NULL),(46444,5839,51063,'2012-08-08 22:05:34','Not really a bug?  Marked as such',NULL,NULL),(46445,5840,51063,'2012-08-08 22:07:05','bumpity? ',NULL,NULL),(46446,5958,51063,'2012-08-08 22:11:15','[quote=yamchan07bb]... I think I should have worded that better, updated the OP :hmmm:\r\n\r\nAs far as I can tell, you\'re in the same boat as everybody, regardless of monitor size.\r\n\r\nAll tabs have a limited width, they do not show the full title, while the titlebar will only show the current page title (Chrome doesn\'t even have a titlebar, for example):\r\n\r\n[b]IE[/b]\r\nFew tabs, titles are truncated anyway\r\n[URL=http://imgbox.com/adhUKxHk][IMG]http://t.imgbox.com/adhUKxHk.jpg[/IMG][/URL]\r\nMany tabs, titles are truncated even more\r\n[URL=http://imgbox.com/acf2BuaI][IMG]http://t.imgbox.com/acf2BuaI.jpg[/IMG][/URL]\r\n\r\n[b]Chrome[/b]\r\nThis behavior is the same across all browsers, unless you have custom settings to allow wider tabs or multi-tab-rows\r\n[URL=http://imgbox.com/acdTYp0e][IMG]http://t.imgbox.com/acdTYp0e.jpg[/IMG][/URL]\r\n\r\nGetting rid of the [c