ease don\'t forget that these badges and credits are only valid untill we officially transfer to this site and abandon the old one. Once that happens all your stats on the old site will be transfered to this one and you will only have as many credits as you saved up on the old site.',NULL,NULL),(47363,6055,51063,'2012-08-22 15:00:46','Did I not say that already?  LOL',NULL,NULL),(47364,6055,94804,'2012-08-22 16:09:16','too bad, though resonable, I kinda liked being a millionaire (although I\'ve got nothing to complain about on the \"old\" site)',NULL,NULL),(47365,6055,171777,'2012-08-22 16:38:50','[quote=GaryE,f3055,27363]Did I not say that already?  LOL[/quote]\r\nLol sry GaryE my bad. Missed that part. Been swimming this morning. Chlorine levels are playing tricks on my eyes...',NULL,NULL),(47366,6055,51063,'2012-08-22 16:56:37','No worries mate -- just having some fun!  LOL  As I used to say on the old empornium it is nice when questions get answered by more than one person . . . that is a very nice problem to have LOL!',NULL,NULL),(47367,6053,1507,'2012-08-22 19:01:57','[quote=apparition,f3053,27358][url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=95AF_5034A720][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/thumb.php?id=95AF_5034A720[/img][/url]\r\nthe header has overlapping elements, that don\'t overlap using empornium.css.  You are also not using google embeded fonts.[/quote]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n:dunno:\r\n\r\n[b]I am using Opera and the overlapping is not happening to me...  :dunno:\r\n\r\nusb[/b]\r\n\r\n:usb:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL),(47368,6053,51063,'2012-08-22 19:35:34','[quote=apparition,f3053,27358][url=http://xxx.freeimage.us/share.php?id=95AF_5034A720][img]http://xxx.freeimage.us/thumb.php?id=95AF_5034A720[/img][/url]\nthe header has overlapping elements, that don\'t overlap using empornium.css.  You are also not using google embeded fonts.[/quote]\n\nI can duplicate this in Firefox when I make the window narrow enough.  I can post a screenshot if necessary.  I\'m going